 Longmont, Colo.'s Solbourne Computer asvice president of engineering.andP;  Schumacher previously served as president andchief executive officer of  Spatial Technology and spent 27 years in variouspositions at Control Data.andP;  Solbourne made industry headlines a few weeksback by introducing Series4 workstations based on Sun Microsystems' Sparcchip.andO;</TEXT></DOC>